  "instructions": [
    "Heat vegetable oil in a Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add rice flour and fry, stirring constantly, for 2 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and let cool slightly.",
    "Add water to the rice flour mixture and stir until a dough forms.",
    "Knead the dough for 5 minutes until it becomes smooth and pliable.",
    "Divide the dough into 4 equal pieces.",
    "Shape each piece into a ball and then flatten slightly into a disk shape.",
    "Heat the butter in a large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add the avocado hass pulp and sauté for 2 minutes."
